KW  - Mispricing
KW  - Liquidity
AB  - We investigate the impact of the likeability and pronounceability of stock ticker symbols on firm value. Using a unique, comprehensive dataset with hand-collected ratings of ticker symbols, we find that higher likeability of ticker symbols leads to higher Tobin׳s Q. The pronounceability of ticker symbols has a similar but weaker effect. Further evidence suggests that the effect is possibly due to the impact of ticker symbols on stock liquidity or mispricing or both.
ER  - 
